"\n"
"Try to distribute your products across your packages so that they weigh less "
"than %(max_weight)s %(unit)s or choose another carrier."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Prøv at fordele dine produkter på flere pakker, så hver pakke vejer mindre "
"end %(max_weight)s %(unit)s, eller vælg et andet transportfirma."

