"The total weight of your transfer is too heavy for the heaviest available "
"shipping method."
msgstr ""
"Den samlede vægt af forsendelsen overstiger den maksimalt tilladte vægt for "
"den tungeste tilgængelige forsendelsesmetode."

#. module: delivery_sendcloud
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/delivery_sendcloud/models/delivery_carrier.py:0
msgid ""
"There are no shipping products available, please update the 'Shipping From' "
"field or activate suitable carriers in your sendcloud account"
msgstr ""
"Der er ingen forsendelsesprodukter tilgængelige. Opdatér feltet "
"\"Forsendelse fra\", eller aktivér de relevante forsendelsesfirmaer i din "
"SendCloud-konto"

#. module: delivery_sendcloud
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/delivery_sendcloud/models/delivery_carrier.py:0
msgid ""
"There is no rate available for this order with the selected shipping product."
msgstr ""
"Der er ingen takst tilgængelig for det valgte forsendelsesprodukt til denne "
"ordre."

#. module: delivery_sendcloud
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/delivery_sendcloud/models/sendcloud_service.py:0
msgid ""
"There is no shipping method available for this order with the selected "
"carrier"
msgstr ""
"Der er ingen forsendelsesmetode tilgængelig for denne ordre med den valgte "
"leverandør"

#. module: delivery_sendcloud
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/delivery_sendcloud/models/sendcloud_service.py:0
msgid ""
"There is no shipping method available for this picking with the selected "
"carrier"
msgstr ""
"Ingen forsendelsesmetode er tilgængelig for denne ordre med den valgte "
"leverandør"

#. module: delivery_sendcloud
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/delivery_sendcloud/models/sendcloud_service.py:0
msgid ""
"There's no method with matching weight range for packages :\n"
"%s\n"
"You can either choose another carrier, change your filters or redefine the "
"content of your package(s)."
msgstr ""
"Der findes ingen metode med et passende vægtinterval for pakkerne:\n"
"%s\n"
"Du kan enten vælge en anden leverandør, ændre dine filtre eller justere "
"indholdet af pakkerne."

#. module: delivery_sendcloud
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/delivery_sendcloud/models/sendcloud_service.py:0
msgid ""
"There's no shipping method matching all your selected filters for this "
"picking/order."
msgstr ""
"Der findes ingen forsendelsesmetode for denne ordre, som opfylder alle de "
"valgte filtre."

#. module: delivery_sendcloud
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/delivery_sendcloud/models/delivery_carrier.py:0
msgid "There's no unit of measure with the name \"%s\"."
msgstr "Der findes ingen måleenhed med navnet \"%s\"."

